        <p>These <a href="ch71s13.html#MonstersS95">sphinxes</a> are the female counterparts of <a href="ch71s13.html#MonstersS99">androsphinxes</a>.<a href="img/MonstersS.Gynosphinx.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersS.Gynosphinx.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
        <div class="sect4" lang="en">
