          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS108"/>
          <p>In close combat, <a href="ch71s13.html#MonstersS107">gynosphinxes</a> use their powerful claws to flay the flesh from their enemies. Despite their deadly nature, they prefer to avoid combat whenever possible.</p>
          <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
            <div class="titlepage"/>
            <a name="id2190606"/>
            <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
              <div class="keyword">other</div>
            </div>
